$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.I need to find another security chip. I’m sorry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.I’ll get you out as soon as I can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.I’ll get you out as soon as I can.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,ba,ex.Get to work Bradley. Unlock these doors and let’s get this over with.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,sh,op.There’s a dead body in the corner!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.You don’t have to be down here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,an,op.I can handle it. I want to help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.There are 4 red slots. I wonder if this is some sort of high-tech lock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,wo,op.Father? Is that you? Why did you not come last night? Is Mother home yet?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,sa,op.Please Father! I need a blessing. Why did you not bless me last night?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sh,op.It sounds like a girl. What the fuck is going on in there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,sa,op.I can hear you Father. Please come to me tonight. I’ve been a good girl.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.This isn’t buddie. I am... I am a Saint Dame University student... I’m studying to be a wizard or whatever.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,cl.Father does not want us talking to you. Please leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Are you okay in there? Do you need help?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,ex.Don’t listen to him Violet. He is trying to decieve you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,fr,op.Do you think he can give us a blessing?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,cl.He is not one of us. Only Father can give us a blessing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,op.When Buddie comes he will shoot you. We are not afraid of you demon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.I’m not a demon! I’m just a guy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.What kind of cult was Parker running?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Who are these girls? Priests don’t have kids... right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op.Or did Father parker have kids and is hiding them?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,wo,ex.Elizabeth. I don’t think he is a demon. Perhaps he can bless us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Yeah. I totally can. My blessing spell is at level 99.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,op.He speaks like a buffoon Violet. Surely he does not possess the ability to bless us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,ba,ex.Guy... Do you have the blessing tool?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,an,ex.The rod of discipline... Do you have the rod!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,op.Violet! Stop it. You can not trust him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,op.Unlock the door and I’ll show it to you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,ba,op.We do not open the door. You must come to us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,wo,op.No Elizabeth, he can help us. We are in need of a blessing. Are you not afraid Elizabeth?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,cl.I will gladly risk strengthening the cursed than let a demon take me away to be tortured.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.I’m not a demon dammit! And I’m not going to torture anyone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,cl.My name is Brad. And no offense, but you sound like a real bitch Elizabeth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,wo,ex.He is a blasphemer Violet. Can’t you see!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,fr,op.Brad. If you are truly able to bless us, I know God will guide you to open these doors.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.Uh no. It’s Brad... The SDU student from earlier.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,sa,op.Brad. Is it true? Is Father Parker really dead?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,ba,op.Don’t be sad Elizabeth. Buddie will find us another priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.Actually. Now that you mention it. I am studying to be a priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,op.You told us you were studying to be a wizard.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,cl.I’ve never heard of such a thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,wo,op.Maybe you can use your powers to help us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,cl.You know. I just might be up to the task.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,ex.Violet! He is trying to trick us! You are not thinking clearly.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,sa,op.It’s the baby Violet. Your burden is clouding your judgement.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,ba,ex.A seed has been planted inside of me. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "El,an,cl.We need a real priest. Not a wizard.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.Hey! I can say with all honestly that I have just as much powers as your stupid priest.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,wo,op.Maybe he can help. What’s the harm?");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.There is a big stone pillar in the way. It’s too big to move. Maybe I can destroy it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.These two doors were locked with security chips.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,wo,op.What the hell is this place? What did Father Parker do down here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,ex.Behind those two doors are Parker’s sex slaves.");

You look eager to visit those chamber girls.
I have come to give you some bad news.
<wordwrap>This update has ended. So you can go in there and talk to the girls, but nothing is going to happen until the next update.
<wordwrap>For now, I am going to go back into the woods with my brethren.
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,wo,op.Mendel! What are you doing in here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.What’s going on Buddie. Talk to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,wo,op.This isn’t what it looks like. Whatever Brad told you, it isn’t true.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,ma,op.There are girls locked in our basement!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,ex.Those girls have a curse. And Parker was saving them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,sh,op.Oh my god. Of course! Violet and Elizabeth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,wo,op.Those girls were a part of our outreach program and went missing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,wo,op.The police questioned us, but no leads were found.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,wo,op.It was assumed they ran away from home. A common problem among troubled individuals in the church’s outreach program.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,cl.They were looking for help and found it. You’d never understand what’s going on here Mendel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.We need to find Parker. He can explain everything.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,wo,ex.The nuns? Sister Judy, Sister Katherine... Mother Superior?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.Mother Superior knows. She is helping Parker.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.We need to get to that bridge.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.We can’t go to the authorities now. Not with all this mess going on.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fl,ex.It looks like you have a clean up job of your own Mendel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,ex.Listen. I don’t know what you people are up to or why you killed Denny. But we need to solve this... without involving the authorities.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,op.And how do you plan to do that?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Huh? Let’s be honest, she can’t even handle herself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.Not with you Brad. There is another person.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,op.You just had to tell someone didn’t you Brad?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.He was threatening us. This makes us even.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ma,op.No they're not! There is no curse!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ma,op.I’m not going to let those girls leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.Don’t tell me. Tell Mendel. He’s not going to let you get away with this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,an,cl.You’re a pain in the ass. You know that right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sh,op.Oh shit! Violet’s door is open! I’m too late!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.This is it Val. Parker was keeping the girls locked down here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,wo,op.What the hell? Why is Violet’s door open?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,fl,cl.Oh Mendel... How could you let this happen?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,ex.Hey! This is all out of my control. We all have something to hide.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,wo,op.Is there someone in that locked room?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,an,op.Open the damn door and let her out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,op. Val. Can I ask you something?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sa,ex.Did you know that Tillman and Andy were making Serum?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,cl.I don’t want to lie to you Dear. It’s something I suspected.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,cl.I couldn’t... I didn’t want the school to suffer another hit.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,ex.It’s hard to watch something you’ve worked so hard to build fall right in front of you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,ex.I’d do anything to protect our school. You understand that right?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.I know Val. You’re the best thing that ever happened to ESU. Everyone loves you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,sa,cl.Not for long I’m afraid. I’ve reached the end of my run. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.No matter what happens I’ll always love you Val.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,fr,cl.If only I wasn’t married to your Brother.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,fr,op.I was always jealous of him ever since the two of you met.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Va,fr,ex.I think right now the only thing we need to worry about is getting out of here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Bu,ba,ex.I’ll deal with him. You’ve done good Brad.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,sa,op.Father told me the bad man is coming.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,ex.Simon! Andy! ... Go hide in the next room and make some noise. When Tillman turns the corner, I’ll shoot him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ti,ma,op.Did you put the girl in there?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,ha,op.I found a toothbrush under my bed!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,sh,op.I didn’t mean to! It slipped out of my hand!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sh,op.Well... Now what the hell do we do?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.Calm down Simon! It was an accident.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,wo,op.Buddie is still out there! And we don’t know what happened to him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,sh,ex.Simon and I found a room... I think it’s a processing facility for separating Serum from the water!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.Yeah I know. I saw it earlier.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,wo,ex.It looked like the security shutdown was messing with the computer.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,op.Shit! Violet is trapped and I destroyed one of the security chips.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,op.Maybe Buddie has the chips from Mendel’s door.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,sa,ex.I’d offer to help, but I can’t hack this security system. This place must have cost Parker a lot of money.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "An,sh,op.Oh god. I can’t stay here with that bloody mess.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,an,op.I’ve got the right door Brad. As soon as you unlock the door I’ll be ready to stop Mendel from escaping.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,ba,ex.Run upstairs Violet. We need to deal with Mendel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Vi,sh,op.Oh my god! Is he going to be okay?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,wo,ex.He’ll be fine Violet. Just run upstairs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Si,ma,op.Come out Mendel! Don’t make us come get you!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Ba,ma,op.No funny business Steedly! We won't hesitate to blow your head off!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,sh,op.What the hell did you do to Tillman!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,sh,op.What the fuck is wrong with you people!?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Am,ma,op.You better shut up Mendel! We have one bullet left just for you!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,an,ex.We’ll send the cops. But you’re not coming with us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Me,an,op.Fine! Don’t aim that gun at me!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "Br,sh,op.Okay. That’s the grossest thing I’ve ever seen.");
